{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1879"},"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","text":"MLNAnnotationView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A string identifying the annotation view to be reused."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This string is the same one you specify when initially returning the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation view object using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"identifier"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An annotation view object with the given identifier, or ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if no","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such object exists in the reuse queue.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For performance reasons, you should generally reuse ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects for identical-looking annotations in your map views. Dequeueing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"saves time and memory during performance-critical operations such as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scrolling.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","type":"topic","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic"}}}